 high-latency neural networks. At the\nsame time, we outperform state-of-the-art asynchronous approaches up to 24% in\nprediction accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 08:39:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2020 15:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-20"}
