th (SPL). Our method also generalizes to new robot embodiments never\nused during training.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 12:30:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Feb 2022 08:10:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-21"}
